<li class='cover' id='bookCover_36528149'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/36528149-padmini"><img alt="Padmini: The Spirited Queen of Chittor" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1509719418l/36528149._SX98_.jpg" />
